“We depend on nature to survive but nature doesn’t really need us.”

From a young age, the importance of the environment was clear to HSH Prince Albert II of Monaco thanks both to his parents passionate pursuit of the subject and his childhood by the Mediterranean sea. He took the values he learned in this time and is using them to unite people around ocean preservation, earning him the nickname ‘The Green Prince’. https://cnb.cx/2Jm5naJ...